SUMMARY:Aspen to Pittock Out-N-Back +Coffee!
DESCRIPTION:Portland Trail Runners\nJoin us for an out-and-back run along the Wildwood Trail! We'll start from the Aspen trailhead\, climbing up\, Up\, UP to Pittock. After we catch our breath and some breathtaking views\, we will turn back around for the (more) fun descent back to start. **5 miles total\, 907' elevation gain**\n\nThe route:\n[https://ridewithgps.com/routes/40977404](https://ridewithgps.com/routes/40977404)\n\n*Want a shorter option?*\nTurn back at anytime to start\; from NW Cornell is about **3 miles**\n\n**Meetup:**\nAt the Aspen Trailhead\, near the intersection of NW Aspen Ave and NW Franklin Ct. Mind your valuables in your vehicles!\n\n**What to bring:**\n\n* Coffee cup/travel mug\n\n**Post Run**\nAs always\, we will bring post-run coffee. If you have a snack you want to share\, great! Or if you'd like\, you can Venmo a couple bucks to the coffee fund (@JeffMonaghanPDX)\, but there's absolutely no expectation for you to bring anything other than yourself\, nor is there any expectation for contributions - just come run with us!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/portland-trail-runners-group/events/312564829/
