SUMMARY:🎤 PTR Karaoke Night: Jeff & Julie are getting Married! 🎉
DESCRIPTION:Portland Trail Runners\n**Jeff and Julie met through PTR\, and now they’re tying the knot! Come join us for a casual\, fun-filled evening to celebrate their upcoming wedding\, connect with fellow runners\, and sing your heart out (or cheer from the crowd!)**\n\n**This is a low-key\, optional night of good(?) music\, great company\, and celebration. Start thinking about what songs you want to sing\, and come be part of the fun! 💍🎶**\n\n**Apologies in advance to both Jeff and Sarah who loathe karaoke! 🙃**
